  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741400/extras/a7c53238e58f40d45794184def9bbbfc.avif?t=1762881802\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drop Racing</strong> <strong>is a block-based game with a racing mindset: the winner is whoever lands all the pieces on the track first.</strong><br>Each track is a fixed sequence that is the same for everyone.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Identical sequences</strong> for fair competition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pace and speed</strong> that escalate with your play — pieces rise and fall <strong>gaining speed</strong> as you pick up the pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No hold</strong>, classic style (following the sequence is part of the challenge)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lap marker:</strong> a <strong>two-block</strong> piece marks the start of each lap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choice of rules:</strong> <strong>Original</strong> (with boosts and lives) or <strong>Classic</strong> (pure)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Modes:</strong> Single race, Championships and Time Attack with lap recording</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Detailed leaderboards</strong> for times per track and per lap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content included:</strong> hand-crafted tracks, tracks with intelligent randomisation and <strong>customisable teams</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No grind:</strong> tracks and teams available from the start</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music:</strong> in-game tracks or option to <strong>use your own</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay 